<m1><styl>hed,2,20,1,jam<ql>
<m0>Garcetti faces tough re-election bid<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.35 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .343 INCHES<m2><ql>
